column5: ANY NEWS ON THE WALLEYE BITE ON QUINTE?
Pictures & message of last weeks action herehttp://groups.msn.com/McQonFishing/shoebox.msnw
Lots going on in the Bay of Qunite. Was there 2 weekends ago and got 27 fish in 2.5 days. Report posted that someone got 22 fish on Sunday. Fishing is hot. Well worth a trip. Cheers, Mike
Have a look at:www.quintefishing.com. Lots going on David Delcloo aka Superdad
